latestIgtvVideos.title: Macy’s & Chanel
latestIgtvVideos.caption: I felt like taking a walk down memory lane and came across some good old work pics! Macy's, and in fact the entire Woodfield Mall has always been a second home to me. It's a bittersweet feeling to see everyone in pics because it reminds me of the good times, but then it poses a question...when will I see everyone again? :-( I wanted to share a short video which is a compilation of random work days. Hope you all like it, maybe it will  remind you all of something sweet during the non-quarantine era, lol!
